"All personal data will be stored on secure servers in the UK. It may also"
" be stored outside of Europe,\n"
"    where it could be viewed by our staff or specialist providers."
msgstr "Bydd yr holl ddata personol yn cael eu storio ar weinyddion diogel yn y DU. Gellir eu storio y tu allan i Ewrop hefyd, lle y bydd ein staff neu ddarparwyr arbenigol yn gallu eu gweld. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:204
msgid ""
"By submitting your personal data, you agree to information being "
"recorded, used and stored\n"
"    as outlined in this Privacy Statement."
