"        and whether they are authorised to act on their behalf.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        They must also agree a password to verify the identity of the "
"third-party if they contact the service again."
msgstr "Bydd CLA yn cydnabod trydydd parti syín cysylltu ar ran person arall. Maeín rhaid iír trydydd parti ddangos bod ganddynt yr awdurdod priodol i weithredu ar eich rhan. Rhaid i CLA gofnodiír berthynas rhwng y trydydd parti aír unigolyn syín gofyn am gyngor ac a ywír trydydd parti wediíi awdurdodi i weithredu ar ei ran. Hefyd rhaid i CLA gytuno ar gyfrinair er mwyn gwirio hunaniaeth y trydydd parti os bydd yn cysylltu ‚ír gwasanaeth eto."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:279
msgid "Outgoing Communications"
msgstr "Anfon negeseuon allan"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:281
msgid "<abbr>CLA</abbr> may need to contact you directly."
msgstr "Maeín bosibl y bydd angen i CLA gysylltu ‚ chiín uniongyrchol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:283
msgid ""
"In order to protect privacy <abbr>CLA</abbr> will always check with you "
"what forms of outgoing communication are acceptable and appropriate and "
"whether messages can be left."
msgstr "Er mwyn diogelu preifatrwydd, bydd CLA bob amser yn gofyn pa ddulliau o gyfathrebu ‚ chi syín dderbyniol a phriodol ac a allwn ni adael negeseuon. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:285
msgid "When making outgoing calls to you <abbr>CLA</abbr> will ensure that:"
msgstr "Pan fydd CLA yn eich ffonio, bydd yn sicrhau: "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:288
msgid ""
"Call backs are only made where you have agreed to this. Authorised third "
"parties\n"
"            acting on your behalf can give agreement."
msgstr "Mai dim ond os ydych chi wedi cytuno ar hynny y byddwn niín ffonioín Ùl. Gall trydydd parti gytuno ar hyn os yw wediíi awdurdodi i weithredu ar eich rhan."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:292
msgid ""
"Where a call back is made to you and there is no answer and a message "
"taker is available,\n"
"            no message will be left unless you have previously given "
"specific instructions that this would be acceptable."
msgstr "Os ywín ffonioín Ùl ac nad oes ateb, a bod recordydd negeseuon ar gael, na fydd yn gadael neges oni bai eich bod wedi rhoi cyfarwyddiadau penodol cyn hynny fod hyn yn dderbyniol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:296
msgid ""
"Where the phone is answered and someone other than you answers the phone "
"and says that you are\n"
"            unavailable or asks who is calling, <abbr>CLA</abbr> will "
"state that the call is confidential and will not say\n"
"            that they are calling from <abbr>CLA</abbr>."
msgstr "Os bydd rhywun heblaw chiín ateb y ffÙn ac yn dweud nad ydych chi ar gael neuín gofyn pwy syín galw, y bydd CLA yn dweud bod yr alwad yn gyfrinachol ac na fydd yn dweud ei fod yn ffonio o CLA."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:306
msgid "How we use cookies"
msgstr "Sut yr ydym yn defnyddio cwcis"

