"Help your <abbr>PC</abbr> or digital device to interact with us more "
"quickly"
msgstr "Helpuích cyfrifiadur personol neu ddyfais ddigidol i ryngweithio ‚ niín fwy cyflym "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:316
msgid ""
"Measure how you use our service so it can be updated and improved based "
