#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:317
msgid ""
"Remember the notifications you‚Äôve seen so that we don‚Äôt show them to you "
"again"
msgstr "Cofioír negeseuon yr ydych chi wediíu gweld fel na fyddwn niín eu dangos i chi eto"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:319
msgid ""
"Remember how you progress through our service. These cookies don't store "
"your personal\n"
"      data and are deleted once you've completed the service."
msgstr "Cofioír camau yr ydych chiín eu cymryd drwy ein gwasanaeth. Nid ywír cwcis hyn yn storioích data personol a byddan nhwín cael eu dileu ar Ùl i chi orffen defnyddioír gwasanaeth."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:323
msgid ""
"Protect your security by ensuring that third parties cannot create sites "
"that pose as\n"
"      a gov.uk service in an attempt to gather your information."
msgstr "Eich cadwín ddiogel drwy sicrhau na fydd trydydd parti yn gallu creu gwefannau syín honni bod yn wasanaeth gov.uk er mwyn casgluích gwybodaeth. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:328
msgid ""
"You can read more about\n"
"    <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/help/cookies\"  rel=\"external\" "
