"          or <abbr title=\"The Ministry of Justice\">MoJ</abbr>"
msgstr "Sefydliadau ymchwil allanol syín gweithio iír LAA neuír Weinyddiaeth Cyfiawnder "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:362
msgid ""
"To inform future government policy on legal aid. Such research will not "
