#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:453
msgid ""
"If you gave us enough information to identify you, <abbr>CLA</abbr> will "
"send you your personal information as soon as\n"
"    possible but within a maximum of 40 days."
msgstr "Os byddwch chi wedi rhoi digon o wybodaeth iích adnabod, bydd CLA yn anfon eich gwybodaeth bersonol atoch chi cyn gynted ‚ phosibl ac o fewn 40 diwrnod ar y mwyaf."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:457
msgid ""
"You can contact us by email at <a class=\"email\" "
"href=\"mailto:data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk\">data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk</a>"
" or in writing to"
msgstr "Gallwch chi gysylltu ‚ ni drwyír e-bost yn data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk neu drwy lythyr yn "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:471
msgid "Requests to delete personal data"
